{"tid":465714,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去旅行唔會去返同一個地方","createTime":"2017-11-11T19:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T10:58:24.000Z","uid":29835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"78723c9b1768b53f36d1a3c857af33051d6aae5b","tid":465714,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:31:57.000Z","msg":"無論目的如何<br />\n例如去完環歐遊<br />\n你屋企人叫你陪佢去歐洲咁<br />\n<br />\n當然工作關係無得推啦<br />\n但有得俾你揀你都會選擇唔去一個你去過嘅地方"},{"pid":"b795ac419c811c7939ba5c4c47d21e41728ae090","tid":465714,"uid":74851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:45:40.000Z","msg":"一次未必睇得晒<br />\n去多次可能會搵返啲未去過既地方"},{"pid":"173080dce07349de209a5b50123ae1410150948f","tid":465714,"uid":8345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T22:03:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ce1e725d3490586bb49396158450dd15c965148","tid":465714,"uid":146924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T22:27:47.000Z","msg":"鍾意嗰個地方就會想再去多幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da8c3c40b864f7000dbee19ca72599bab8de801","tid":465714,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a12971fc6fda3ab9432529f565472a14023156","tid":465714,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:27:06.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117425f22a17a84a2b29382db1adc91927263f71","tid":465714,"uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"日本好難唔去多過一次<br />\n歐洲就算 返工假期好珍貴"},{"pid":"a09c6f3ebac7caa8b759810f482aca2cff449ba1","tid":465714,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"我，不過國家計，去完日本, 泰國唔會再去。"},{"pid":"1ad6b7bb5fae01a3507d0c68e6efcf14f96ab37f","tid":465714,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本好難唔去多過一次<br />\n歐洲就算 返工假期好珍貴</blockquote><br />\n平均每年三四次旅行<br />\n一定有一次去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b71efd99353479b67565aea98d101ea320f3b9","tid":465714,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:35:55.000Z","msg":"通常窮撚先會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404ea29269045a091eaa13da0f9c37d68fa7b142","tid":465714,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"我會<br />\n例如我已經去過果個觀點<br />\n下次fd想去我會話果度無咩特別唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1176fe05cf4317b41c2e6a512e877d7051d76f8","tid":465714,"uid":54593,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"去旅行係為左集郵既人 就會咁諗"},{"pid":"771f3bb6af880654f7a78e6d7c6b39979ee0cea7","tid":465714,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"反而想去下面典 nepel<br />\n點知仲貴過日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0662159f5d4e3ab7b9654a33b21bced4b8f08f7e","tid":465714,"uid":9942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行係為左集郵既人 就會咁諗</blockquote><br />\n好有見地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f680394ca43562c197a47df56c064774971c10a","tid":465714,"uid":88888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"第二次個feel 可以好唔同<br />\n總有野你未去過"},{"pid":"e37c92257cb9a795369458c738f75a5c81c40bd6","tid":465714,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80a51cbd73cec2d0e88ae513a6bd04fe999c15d0","tid":465714,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界太大，想趁後生睇多啲先"},{"pid":"1801378fb35e64173a28b0066aeaafcfc49ef9b7","tid":465714,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"鍾意既就會去多次, 唔鍾意先唔會去返同一個地方<br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得用城市計都還好, 如果用國家計, 唔通日本你可以一次去晒咩, 一定會重覆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d117b551ffd0c518f4c2ea209fa0da059cf4da1","tid":465714,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"計地方，以前成日同一個地方去幾次。<br />\n<br />\n依家盡量唔會，寧願做多啲功課 PLAN好啲。<br />\n<br />\n但有啲大城市真係去唔厭，去極都仲有漏網之魚，未去到。<br />\n<br />\n除咗吃喝過週末既景點外 (台北/曼谷)，其他都少去多過兩次。"},{"pid":"ad3f3e03163ec9e020e7c6f59dbb15bfe510b19b","tid":465714,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去旅行係為左集郵既人 就會咁諗</blockquote><br />\n好有見地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多"},{"pid":"7e0a3ae205107cb5779abb756f53e048c8866095","tid":465714,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"就算去香港咁細地方，<br />\n都好多嘢睇啦。<br />\n<br />\n去兩三轉都唔出奇喎。"},{"pid":"afc1e680f09c1cf99b0b1daf02b027ad09f0a2d3","tid":465714,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"的確係集郵心態 好多國家都想去 <br />\n自問時間同錢都有限  唔知去唔去到<br />\n<br />\n一年得十幾日假    最多去兩次旅行<br />\n又唔知撈到幾時會中年失業<br />\n<br />\n所以盡量次次去唔同國家有"}]}